Package: getsat
Title: Retrieving Commonly Used Satellite Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Abdollah", "Jalilian", , "stat4aj@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This R package simplifies access to key satellite data on environmental variables from sources like the Copernicus Atmosphere Monitoring Service, Copernicus Climate Data Store, and Microsoft Planetary Computer. It streamlines data retrieval, processing, and integration, making satellite-based environmental analysis more efficient and accessible.
